<item>
            <title>[SEC-2174] Consider making spring-jdbc and spring-aop optional</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-2174</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This will help with the version mismatch problem with Spring 3.2. Another approach is to possibly use version ranges. However, this makes builds change without making explicit changes (i.e. once Spring releases again a build will be changed)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
