                            <comment id="90564" author="michael.isvy" created="Mon, 3 Jun 2013 15:51:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is my original email, so we can keep track:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If I just declare a spring-security without excluding any dependency, I end up with having spring-tx 3.2.3 and spring-aop 3.0.7 next to each other.&lt;/p&gt;


